data.description: This charming West Arvada home is ready to make yours.  An open and airy main floor living with plenty of natural light leads to an eat-in kitchen with built-in table.  Patio door in the kitchen leads to the large corner lot backyard with mature trees, two storage sheds, and plenty of room for entertaining.  Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms, and a full bathroom.  One bedroom has a convenient large walk-in laundry closet.  The lower level boasts a nice sized family room with built-in shelving, a beautifully remodeled 3/4 bathroom, and a third bedroom. Included solar is paid for.  In ground sprinklers installed in front and back.  Single car garage and extra long driveway could fit your RV or toys! This home is close to trails, parks, the Apex Center, shopping, and schools, and has easy access to I-70! Seller is offering a $10,000 concession at closing for interest rate buy-down or to help cover closing costs.
